project_descr: Preparation of HCFC Phase-out Management Plan (HPMP) Stage-1 for Lebanon

outputs.output_descr: The project will result in the preparation of a comprehensive HPMP (Stage-1) for Lebanon, which will incorporate the strategy and action plan for Lebanon for compliance with the 2013/2015 control targets, which is targeted for submission to the Executive Committee of the Multilateral Fund in 2010.

project_title: preparation of hcfc phase-out management plan (hpmp)
